year: 2023
main_author: "Bin Yu, He Zhao, Tong Zhou, Nianzu Sheng, Xiaofeng Li, Jinlin Xu"
main_contribution: "Proposed a full sharding architecture combining an overlapping network model and virtual accounts to eliminate cross-shard transaction coordination and achieve nearly linear scalability."
